%h1(style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 1.77em;")
  ScoutActivity Report

%h2(style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: left;line-height: 1.5em;font-size: 1em;font-weight:500")
  In the past week, there were

%table.table(style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;width:200px;border:none;")
  %tr
    %th(style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;border:none;padding:0.15em;text-align: left;")
      New Users
    %td(style="border:none;padding:0.15em;text-align:right;")  
      = @new_users_count
  %tr
    %th(style="border:none;padding:0.15em;text-align: left;")
      Total Users
    %td(style="border:none;padding:0.15em;text-align:right;")  
      = @total_users_count
  %tr
    %th(style="border:none;padding:0.15em;text-align: left;")
      Active Users
    %td(style="border:none;padding:0.15em;text-align:right;")  
      = @active_users_count
  %tr
    %th(style="border:none;padding:0.15em;text-align: left;")
      New Units
    %td(style="border:none;padding:0.15em;text-align:right;")  
      = @new_units_count
  %tr
    %th(style="border:none;padding:0.15em;text-align: left;")
      New Activities
    %td(style="border:none;padding:0.15em;text-align:right;")  
      = @new_activities_count


  / %p(style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Sego=e UI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;")
  /   There are currently a total of
  /   %strong= @total_active_users_count
  /   users


  / %p(style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Sego=e UI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;margin-top:30px")
  /   The break-down of Plans in-use:
  / %table.table(style="width:150px;border:none;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;")
  /   - @plans_hash.each do |plan, count|
  /     %tr
  /       %th(style="border:none;padding:0.15em;text-align: left;")
  /         = plan
  /       %td(style="border:none;padding:0.15em;text-align:right;")
  /         = count

  / %p(style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Sego=e UI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; margin-top: 30px")
  /   There are currently
  /   %strong= number_with_delimiter(@total_products_count)
  /   products being monitored and there have been
  /   %strong= number_with_delimiter(@total_reviews_count)
  /   reviews collected.